data.name: TechnicPrivatePermissions.ToolTip
data.value: These are packs used only on one specific server. Their intention is to allow servers to customize their server experience without compromising the ease of installation offered by the Technic launcher.

data.name: PrivateFTBPack.ToolTip
data.value: These are packs used only on one specific server. Their intention is to allow servers to customize their server experience without compromising the ease of installation offered by the FTB launcher. These modpacks must only be accessible behind a application process of some form. The code may not be posted publicly.​
